<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id2177358">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id2020653"><p id="fs-id2229436">Chewing a bite of bread mixes it with saliva and facilitates its chemical breakdown. This is <em data-effect="italics">most likely</em> due to the fact that ________.</p>
